This is the area corresponding to the North Anchorage Sea, it is situated directly north the naval base and is unlocked from the start of the game.<br>
There is one repair dock on this hexagon and is expandable up to two.<br>
:Clearing the first map of this area (V8-1), alongside [[Kancolle Kai:Sandbox/Area 9#/V9-1|V9-1]] gives access to [[KanColle Kai:Sandbox/Area 11#/V11-1|V11-1]] ('''中部西海域''').
:Fully clearing this area gives access to [[KanColle Kai:Sandbox/Area 3#/V3-1|V3-1]] ('''北方海域''').

